<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="A layout example that shows off a responsive product landing page.">
  <title>VoicePDF</title>




  <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/pure/0.6.0/pure-min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.css">
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag '_bootstrap' %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'parallax.css' %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'jquery.min.js' %>

</head>
<body>









<div class="header">
  <div class="home-menu pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal pure-menu-fixed">
    <a class="pure-menu-heading" href="">VoicePDF</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="splash-container">
  <div class="splash">
    <h1 class="splash-head">VoicePDF</h1>
    <p class="splash-subhead">
      Try it out!
      Say Log in or Sign Up
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="#" class="pure-button pure-button-primary login-button" id="login-button">Log In!</a>
        <%= render 'shared/login_form' %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-wrapper">
  <div class="content">
    <h2 class="content-head is-center">The Easy To Use Voice Controlled Reader</h2>
    <div class="pure-g">
      <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">

        <h3 class="content-subhead">
          <i class="fa fa-rocket"></i>
          Get Started Quickly
        </h3>
        <p>
          It takes seconds to sign up. With VoicePDF you can store and view all your PDF files in one place! With an easy to upload form,
          uploading your PDF files to view couldn't be any easier! Student?
          Why Carry around a huge book when you can get the pdf version and add it to your library. Business Personnel? Upload your next speech
          or presentation, and have it safely stored and easy to access. VoicePDF is an easy to use site for everyone!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
        <h3 class="content-subhead">
          <i class="fa fa-mobile"></i>
          Responsive Layouts
        </h3>
        <p>
         Not only can you use VoicePDF on your Mac or Windows, VoicePDF works on all Android and iOS tablets and smartphones!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
        <h3 class="content-subhead">
          <i class="fa fa-th-large"></i>
          Build Your Library
        </h3>
        <p>
          After uploading your PDF file, you'll be redirected to your library where you can choose which file you want to view!
          <br/>
          Store all your PDFs in easy to use environment. Store comic books, tutorial books, cook books, presentations, you name it!
          Keep it all in one place.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
        <h3 class="content-subhead">
          <i class="fa fa-check-square-o"></i>
          Easy To Learn Commands
        </h3>
        <p>
          Its easy! There are but a few of commands needed to use the voice aspect of this site.
          Its also completely optional! <br/> You can simply deny access to your microphone and still use the many features of the site!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ribbon l-box-lrg pure-g">
    <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
      <img class="pure-img-responsive" alt="File Icons" width="300" src="">
    </div>
    <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">

      <h2 class="content-head content-head-ribbon">Try It Out!</h2>

      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod
        tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam,
        quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo
        consequat. Duis aute irure dolor.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <a name="signup"></a>
    <h2 class="content-head is-center">Sign Up!</h2>

    <div class="pure-g">
      <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-2-5">
        <%= render 'shared/new_user_form' %>
      </div>

      <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-3-5">
        <h4>Contact Us</h4>
        <p>
          At VoicePDF, our first thought is you! If you have any questions, advice, or just want to say hi, feel free to contact us!
        </p>


      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="footer l-box is-center">
    <p id="left-p">Â©2015 Gil Figueroa</p>
  </div>

</div>





<%= javascript_include_tag 'parallax.js' %>
<%= javascript_include_tag 'annyang.min' %>
</body>
</html>
